	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You unleash your magic upon your target as you viciously insult them.</em></p><p><strong>Wisdom Save</strong> </p><p>Your target must be able to hear you, but does not need to understand you.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 1d4 psychic]] psychic damage,* and has disadvantage on their next attack roll.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> No effect.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*At Higher Levels:</strong> This spell's damage increases by [[/damage 1d4 psychic]] when you reach a total character or creature level of 5th level ([[/damage 2d4 psychic]]), 11th level ([[/damage 3d4 psychic]]), and 17th level ([[/damage 4d4 psychic]]).</p>",
			"chat": "<p><strong>Wisdom Save</strong></p><p>Your target must be able to hear you, but does not need to understand you.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 1d4 psychic]] psychic damage,* and has disadvantage on their next attack roll.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> No effect.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*At Higher Levels:</strong> This spell's damage increases by [[/damage 1d4 psychic]] when you reach a total character or creature level of 5th level ([[/damage 2d4 psychic]]), 11th level ([[/damage 3d4 psychic]]), and 17th level ([[/damage 4d4 psychic]]).</p>"
